ValuesEO.getConfigurationList.description: store a list EO config objects. Without parameter the available config classes names will be set. Without configFilter all available keys will be returned, otherwise only the filtered result.

ValuesEO.getConfigurationKeys.description: store the names of a EO config list. Without configType parameter the available config classes names will be set. Without configFilter all available keys will be returned, otherwise only the filtered result.

ValuesEO.getConfiguration.description: store the values of a EO configuration. All parameters have to be set.
